item_long_description: THE MULTIPLIER IS USUALLY .10 - .167  HRS PER STONE (60 DIVIDED BY X (HOW MANY PER HOUR) = N THEN DIVIDE N BY 60 TO GET THE MULTIPLIER). TAKE THE AMOUNT OF BLOCKS AND MULTIPLY BY THE MULTIPLER TO GET HOW MANY HOURS IT WILL TAKE TO INSTALL THE MATERIALS
GUYS SHOULD BE ABLE TO CUT 80 LN FT PER DAY
80 SQ FT/DAY W/ MORTAR&120 SQ FT/DAY
LOOK @ THE NOTE ON BASE RUN LAY.
GUYS SHOULD BE ABLE TO INSTALL 20-30 SQ. FT. PER HOUR
